The paper discusses secure distributed cloud storage, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of error-correcting codes and authentication tags suggests that the paper may also belong to the database (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. Finally, the proposal of an efficient scheme for updating parity blocks suggests that the paper may also belong to the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category.
